            "blank_if_zero": 0,
            "readonly": 0,
            "message": "\"* Based on the number of nonconformities and findings during the audit, the Lead Auditor considers the Management system is acceptable.\r\n* The information and evidence about conformity to all requirements of the management system standard is found to be acceptable.\r\n* The Performance monitoring, measuring, reporting and reviewing against key performance objectives and targets wrt Management System Standard is found to be acceptable.\r\n* The ability of the management system to ensure adherence to applicable statutory, regulatory and contractual requirements is found to be acceptable.\r\n* The Operational Controls of clients processes are found to be acceptable\r\n* The Effectiveness of internal auditing and management review is found to be acceptable \r\n* Status of Management responsibility for the clients policies are found acceptable\"",
